  /- It suffices to produce `g : C(X, ‚Ñù‚â•0)` which takes values in `[0,1]` and is constantly `1` on
    `t` such that when composed with the natural embedding of `‚Ñù‚â•0` into `ùïú` lies in the ideal `I`.
